Package: wget2
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: Multi-threaded recursive downloader
 Wget2 is the official successor of Wget.
 .
 It supports new features like HTTP/2, parallel downloads,
 compression, Metalink, OCSP, HSTS, PSL, TFO, TLS
 session resumption, TLS False Start.
 .
 For recursive downloading, Wget2 scans HTML, CSS, Sitemaps, RSS
 and Atom feeds.
